Rules.InvariantScript:
If(
    cmp_GCThemeHeader.ContentWidth > Parent.ScreenWidthBreakpoints.Large,
    ScreenSize.ExtraLarge,
    If(
        cmp_GCThemeHeader.ContentWidth > Parent.ScreenWidthBreakpoints.Medium && cmp_GCThemeHeader.ContentWidth <= Parent.ScreenWidthBreakpoints.Large,
        ScreenSize.Large,
        If(
            cmp_GCThemeHeader.ContentWidth > Parent.ScreenWidthBreakpoints.Small && cmp_GCThemeHeader.ContentWidth <= Parent.ScreenWidthBreakpoints.Medium,
            ScreenSize.Medium,
            If(
                cmp_GCThemeHeader.ContentWidth <= Parent.ScreenWidthBreakpoints.Small,
                ScreenSize.Small
            )
        )
    )
)

If(
    Parent.Width > Parent.ScreenWidthBreakpoints.Large,
    ScreenSize.ExtraLarge,
    If(
        Parent.Width > Parent.ScreenWidthBreakpoints.Medium && Parent.Width <= Parent.ScreenWidthBreakpoints.Large,
        ScreenSize.Large,
        If(
            Parent.Width > Parent.ScreenWidthBreakpoints.Small && Parent.Width <= Parent.ScreenWidthBreakpoints.Medium,
            ScreenSize.Medium,
            If(
                Parent.Width <= Parent.ScreenWidthBreakpoints.Small,
                ScreenSize.Small
            )
        )
    )
)

If(cmp_GCThemeHeader.ContentWidth,
    Average(360 * Switch(Value(lblContentWidthSizing_GCH.Text),  
            ScreenSize.Small, 0.5,  
            ScreenSize.Medium, 0.75,
            ScreenSize.Large, 0.85,  
            1)
    ),
    Average(360 * Switch(Value(lblScreenWidthSizing_GCH.Text),  
            ScreenSize.Small, 0.5,  
            ScreenSize.Medium, 0.75,
            ScreenSize.Large, 0.85,  
            1)
    )
)

If(cmp_GCThemeHeader.LanguageLinkFontSize > 0,
    cmp_GCThemeHeader.LanguageLinkFontSize,
    If(cmp_GCThemeHeader.ContentWidth,
        Average(16 * Switch(Value(lblContentWidthSizing_GCH.Text),  
                ScreenSize.Small, 0.5,  
                ScreenSize.Medium, 0.75,
                ScreenSize.Large, 1,  
                1)
        ),
        Average(16 * Switch(Value(lblScreenWidthSizing_GCH.Text),  
                ScreenSize.Small, 0.5,  
                ScreenSize.Medium, 0.75,
                ScreenSize.Large, 1,  
                1)
        )
    )
)

Sum(AddColumns(Split(Self.Text, ""), "Size", LookUp(cmp_GCThemeHeader.FontSizing, CharFont=Self.Font && CharWeight=Self.FontWeight && Char = Result).Size), Size) * Self.Size + Self.PaddingLeft + Self.PaddingRight

If(cmp_GCThemeHeader.ContentWidth, 
    cmp_GCThemeHeader.ContentWidth, 
    Parent.Width * Switch(Value(lblScreenWidthSizing_GCH.Text),  
        ScreenSize.Small, 0.75,  
        ScreenSize.Medium, 0.75,
        ScreenSize.Large, 0.54,  
        0.54) 
)

Switch(cmp_GCThemeHeader.AppNameTextRole,
    "heading1",
    TextRole.Heading1,
    "heading2",
    TextRole.Heading2,
    "heading3",
    TextRole.Heading3,
    "heading4",
    TextRole.Heading4,
    TextRole.Default
)

If(cmp_GCThemeHeader.AppNameFontSize > 0,
    cmp_GCThemeHeader.AppNameFontSize,
    If(cmp_GCThemeHeader.ContentWidth,
        Average(28 * Switch(Value(lblContentWidthSizing_GCH.Text),  
            ScreenSize.Small, 0.35,  
            ScreenSize.Medium, 0.75,
            ScreenSize.Large, 0.9,  
            1)
        ),
        Average(28 * Switch(Value(lblScreenWidthSizing_GCH.Text),  
            ScreenSize.Small, 0.35,  
            ScreenSize.Medium, 0.75,
            ScreenSize.Large, 0.9,  
            1)
        )
    )
)

If(cmp_GCThemeHeader.ContentWidth, 
    cmp_GCThemeHeader.ContentWidth,
    Parent.Width * Switch(Value(lblScreenWidthSizing_GCH.Text),  
        ScreenSize.Small, 0.75,  
        ScreenSize.Medium, 0.75,
        ScreenSize.Large, 0.54,  
        0.54) 
)
